Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: grasp2alm
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: A package that converts Planck-LevelS beam-related code to python, supporting the computation of Stokes parameter beams from the GRASP beam format, projection onto the HEALPix sphere, conversion to expansion coefficients for spherical harmonics, etc.
Author: Yusuke Takase
Author-email: takase_y@s.okayama-u.ac.jp
License: MIT
Requires-Dist: numpy
Requires-Dist: healpy
Requires-Dist: matplotlib
